explanation.concept_text: Solution This is a special type of Keyhole question, referred to as "Rock Keyholes" . As mentioned in the Keyhole video series, Rock Keyhole questions must be approached cautiously. The primary purpose of Rock Keyhole questions is to consume your time, and so the best way to approach them is to take an educated guess and move on. Here is a refresher of the Rock Keyhole video:
